                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190113-8-off55 t18190113-8-cd56"></join>, thirty-two printed bound books, value 5 l., and fourteen other books, value 14 s.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190113-8-victim142" type="victimName">
                     Stanley 
                     Goddard
                  <interp inst="t18190113-8-victim142" type="surname" value="Goddard"></interp>
